{
  "number": 185,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/185",
  "title": "API Proposal: searchOnEmptyQuery: boolean",
  "body": "``` js\nvar search = instantsearch(appId, apiKey, {\n  searchOnEmptyQuery: false\n});\n```\n\nWhat this would do is not do any search query when the query is empty. This would allow people wanting to build things like https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/83#issuecomment-146159807 more easily.\n\nWhat do you think?\n",
